{"tid":2304361,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"回顧淨係十一月已經發生咁多事，痴孖筋","createTime":"2020-11-28T17:08:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-11T15:38:19.000Z","uid":13586,"like":211,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"9272e12082c9e273a62f4ec08cdf236e799cd33f","tid":2304361,"uid":13586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T17:08:48.000Z","msg":"已經唔係由七一國安法立法開始數，黎智英，十二港人，鍾翰林，狗入蘋果日報，譚得志，各國制裁，各國取消引導條例，英國LOTR同5+1，美國大選...<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">01/11 胡志偉、尹兆堅、黃碧雲、張超雄、郭永健被捕\n03/11 鏗鏘集編導蔡玉玲被捕\n03/11 浸大學生記者鄧澤旻被捕\n05/11 網媒「娛賓」女記者今早被上門拘捕\n05/11 國安處舉報熱線正式啟用\n08/11 周梓樂離世一年\n09/11 前學生動源成員陸海天被捕\n10/11 美國財政部宣布再制裁4名中港官員\n11/11 楊岳橋、郭榮鏗、郭家麒、梁繼昌喪失議員資格\n12/11 民主派立法會議員宣布總辭\n12/11 中大保衛戰一週年\n13/11 加拿大推出移民新措施\n13/11 可立小學教師被教局釘牌\n15/11 前小學教師楊博文被捕\n15/11 記協遊行不獲批\n16/11 安心出行可以下載\n16/11 黃店黃屋台東主等四人被捕\n17/11 沙田區議員李志宏被捕\n18/11 理大圍城一週年\n18/11 許智峯、朱凱廸、陳志全被捕\n19/11 中大畢業遊行\n20/11 國安處進入中大校園蒐證\n20/11 王婆婆王鳳瑤被捕\n21/11 金馬57屆最佳劇情短片《夜更》\n21/11 網台D100主持傑斯被捕\n22/11 確診武肺可一筆過$5000津貼\n22/11 英國國會跨黨派提名王婆婆諾貝爾和平獎\n22/11 王百羽、李軒朗被捕\n23/11 黃之峰、周庭、林朗彥認罪還押至下月中判刑\n23/11 12月書展暫停，延期至明年七月\n24/11 BBC百大女性，周庭榜上有名\n25/11 施政報告，國教借用通識科借屍還魂\n25/11 將會修例公務員宣誓\n27/11 《理大圍城》贏得IDFA最佳剪接獎\n27/11 BE WATER車牌申請失敗\n28/11 警下周起將拘太子站獻花人士\n30/11 十二港人一百日</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n我夠膽寫包單一定有遺漏，真心痴撚線香港，仲可以吃喝玩樂繼續返工，完全當冇事發生，真心做唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n話我正能量撚都要咁講<br />\n明知健康碼、大灣區、明日大嶼、辱警罪之後係咁過，黎明之前嘅黑暗係最撚黑暗，但大家挺住，做得幾多得幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"large\"><span class=\"orange\">五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n香港獨立 唯一出路</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kqm4SNi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkqm4SNi.jpg&h=54a0ae2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://samhighome.files.wordpress.com/2019/11/photo_2019-11-14-20.10.10.jpeg?w=960\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsamhighome.files.wordpress.com%2F2019%2F11%2Fphoto_2019-11-14-20.10.10.jpeg%3Fw%3D960&h=9e8c3a7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://gdb-voanews-com.cdn.ampproject.org/i/s/gdb.voanews.com/BB0B6A0F-48B2-4863-ACCF-E32CF6C488B1_cx0_cy6_cw0_w1080_h608_s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgdb-voanews-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fi%2Fs%2Fgdb.voanews.com%2FBB0B6A0F-48B2-4863-ACCF-E32CF6C488B1_cx0_cy6_cw0_w1080_h608_s.jpg&h=fd8c0bd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pr0xhiW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPr0xhiW.png&h=e85bb282&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1ad48433f2d9830bbb0cce13894cb95554af81c5","tid":2304361,"uid":296600,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T17:14:40.000Z","msg":"其實日日都睇新聞睇到好唔開心"},{"pid":"ca1a54c87f2edb48a01b676351910430358ade8c","tid":2304361,"uid":126648,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T17:15:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54a8d6bc1b2de07a6d9e2cdae13fa4273cfe58de","tid":2304361,"uid":13586,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1ad48433f2d9830bbb0cce13894cb95554af81c5","tid":2304361,"uid":296600,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T17:14:40.000Z","msg":"其實日日都睇新聞睇到好唔開心"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T17:19:07.000Z","msg":"自己有排直頭睇到想揾社工<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d76364a010148f189fe1991d1653f8c76a911eab","tid":2304361,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T17:20:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df4a68b073543e6e54994fe428d1e34cd2e797e5","tid":2304361,"uid":284699,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T17:22:03.000Z","msg":"越近年尾會越多事發生"},{"pid":"8e0efba527914dca4d0d68ed0be24f9343012434","tid":2304361,"uid":13586,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca1a54c87f2edb48a01b676351910430358ade8c","tid":2304361,"uid":126648,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T17:15:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T17:23:53.000Z","msg":"武肺都需要知嘅，跳舞群組咁痴，佢哋又隱暪病史周圍行都死<br />\n<br />\n所以建興隻雞蟲雖然叫雞好仆街，但咁誠實嘅雞蟲真心respect <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但你問我，主次問題我會關注呢啲&gt;武肺"},{"pid":"2babd860ecefca7d5b297953a21879f5f66b32ba","tid":2304361,"uid":13586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T17:26:06.000Z","msg":"已經漏咗今日單有線查唐樓圖則<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e9fa24a38752d64ee7755770bb1c63df96a35a5","tid":2304361,"uid":13586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2babd860ecefca7d5b297953a21879f5f66b32ba","tid":2304361,"uid":13586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T17:26:06.000Z","msg":"已經漏咗今日單有線查唐樓圖則<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T17:26:43.000Z","msg":"同埋佐敦大火"},{"pid":"149ed25f8435b350801df343437b798e1746781e","tid":2304361,"uid":13586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d76364a010148f189fe1991d1653f8c76a911eab","tid":2304361,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T17:20:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.